@startuml
!include ../includes/appsec-style.puml
title AppSec Process 07: DAST Lifecycle (Rapid7 InsightAppSec)

' Purpose: Continuously test running apps for exploitable issues, linked to AppCode for ownership.

start

partition "Plan" {
  :Define targets (URLs/APIs) + credentials;
  :Tag targets with AppCode;
  :Choose scan cadence (per risk tier);
}

partition "Execute" {
  :Run InsightAppSec scan;
  :Capture findings + evidence;
}

partition "Triage" {
  :Validate signal (false positive check);
  :Correlate to AppCode + owner;
  if (Critical/high?) then (Yes)
    :Escalate + set SLA;
  else (No)
    :Backlog with SLA;
  endif
}

partition "Remediate" {
  :Fix code/config;
  :Deploy to test/prod;
}

partition "Verify" {
  :Re-scan to confirm closure;
  :Update metrics (AppCode);
}

note right
Key message: **DAST finds what static scans miss** (auth flows, config, runtime behavior).
end note

stop
@enduml
